
Explicar el juego en el how to.


User press radar to update player locations.

For the example, host is human, the one who joins is a zombie

Check if you have been bitten every 5 seconds, decrease game time every ** seconds




HOST Zombie

Every 5 seconds, send and get locations of all players.
If you bit, select player.


List<Player> players = result.getItems();

			lats.clear();
			lons.clear();

			for (Player p : players) {

				if (p.getGameTitle().equals(gameTitle)) {
					System.out.println("Found players");

					if (p.getIsHuman()) {
						if (p.getUserEmail() != email) {
							lats.add(p.getUserLat());
							lons.add(p.getUserLon());
						} else {

							p.setUserLat(lat);
							p.setUserLon(lon);
						}

					}

				}

			}
			refreshRadar();

HOST Human

Every 5 seconds:

send and get locations of humans.
check if bitten.





